<p></p>
<p>Click the icon Endless, and then click Settings.</p>
<p>In the window that appears, click Printers. To continue, you have to unlock
 this window by clicking on the button that says unlocked in the upper right
 corner and enter your password.</p>
<p>Click the + symbol in the lower left corner of this window.</p>
<p>Then select your printer from the list that appears, and click Add.</p>
<p>You will see the name of your printer already appears in this window. If you
 want to check that your printer is configured correctly, click on the button
 that says Print test page, for a sample sheet printed.</p>
<p>You can close this window.</p>

